annotations.label: Camp
annotations.notes: Rat Spot - Not Very Common You can side climb between rocks and get into a hidden spot nobody ever checks.

annotations.label: Snipe
annotations.notes: Common Spot You are able to peek over the bridge mid map and watch the enemies pushing to the A point.

annotations.label: Snipe
annotations.notes: Counter to bottom side peek - Rare You can sit behind the coal piles, and look right through 2 pillars to get a good shot on anybody camping in the other sides spawn peek
